<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="91600000t" end="135200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">「約定的夢幻島 S2」</p>
<p begin="158800000t" end="198400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">(回想起來了　回想起來了)</p>
<p begin="199200000t" end="238400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">(在那一眨眼間的絕望感覺)</p>
<p begin="239200000t" end="278400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">(即使醒來了　仍然在夢中)</p>
<p begin="279200000t" end="323200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(夢見我們剎那光輝的故事)</p>
<p begin="324000000t" end="363200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(時鐘的秒針)</p>
<p begin="364000000t" end="393200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(請對我報以微笑吧)</p>
<p begin="394000000t" end="454400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(滿腦子心心念念的都是你啊)</p>
<p begin="479600000t" end="518000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(打破冰封三尺的明日吧)</p>
<p begin="518800000t" end="558400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(盡是些絕對不能失去的事物)</p>
<p begin="559200000t" end="598400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(我在命運指引的前路上找到了你)</p>
<p begin="599200000t" end="637200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(如今眼淚已再也沒有意義)</p>
<p begin="638000000t" end="677200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(在飛快地運轉的世界一角)</p>
<p begin="678000000t" end="718800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(有如吶喊一樣呼吸著)</p>
<p begin="719600000t" end="758000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(如能在跨越千千萬萬時光後重逢)</p>
<p begin="758800000t" end="800800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(就在絕望的前方一步笑吧)</p>
<p begin="933600000t" end="958000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">諾曼，是你嗎</p>
<p begin="980400000t" end="990800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="1044000000t" end="1066000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">我很掛念你，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="1072400000t" end="1089200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">看到你沒事真的太好了</p>
<p begin="1090000000t" end="1132000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">我在做夢嗎？諾曼，你竟然還活著</p>
<p begin="1132800000t" end="1144400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">太好了</p>
<p begin="1154800000t" end="1182000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">你真的…真的是諾曼嗎</p>
<p begin="1187600000t" end="1218800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">不會是人有相似或是鬼魂吧</p>
<p begin="1219600000t" end="1243200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">為甚麼？怎麼會</p>
<p begin="1244000000t" end="1266800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">你不是被送出欄了嗎</p>
<p begin="1293200000t" end="1329200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">只有我一個被送往另一個農場</p>
<p begin="1330000000t" end="1340800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">艾瑪，你…</p>
<p begin="1354000000t" end="1388400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">耳朵？我把它留在孤兒院</p>
<p begin="1389200000t" end="1409200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">因此才能逃跑出來</p>
<p begin="1410000000t" end="1429600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">我還把雷帶出來了</p>
<p begin="1430400000t" end="1440800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">雷</p>
<p begin="1464400000t" end="1478400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">你怎麼能這樣</p>
<p begin="1479200000t" end="1501200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">連招呼也不打，就先報仇</p>
<p begin="1521200000t" end="1539600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">出來學會了不少知識吧</p>
<p begin="1540400000t" end="1564800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">對，多虧了你</p>
<p begin="1591200000t" end="1609200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">你沒有死真的太好了</p>
<p begin="1617200000t" end="1630800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">警告你</p>
<p begin="1631600000t" end="1665200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">別再隨便送死，傻瓜諾曼</p>
<p begin="1695600000t" end="1722000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">知道了，傻瓜雷</p>
<p begin="1796800000t" end="1808400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">怎麼會</p>
<p begin="1809200000t" end="1834400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">是…諾曼？</p>
<p begin="1835200000t" end="1872000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">你沒有死？真的是諾曼</p>
<p begin="1872800000t" end="1886000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">真的是諾曼？</p>
<p begin="1895600000t" end="1913200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">諾曼…</p>
<p begin="1918800000t" end="1932800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">太好了　　真的是你嗎</p>
<p begin="1933600000t" end="1946800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">不敢相信</p>
<p begin="1947600000t" end="1970800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">你們都長大了很多</p>
<p begin="1986800000t" end="2001200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">怎麼只有15個人</p>
<p begin="2002000000t" end="2028800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">菲爾他們暫時還在孤兒院</p>
<p begin="2029600000t" end="2050000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">不過一定能把他們救出來</p>
<p begin="2080800000t" end="2092000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">那枝筆呢</p>
<p begin="2092800000t" end="2110800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">沒有指引你們去避難所嗎</p>
<p begin="2111600000t" end="2133600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">那裡已經被農場的人破壞了</p>
<p begin="2134400000t" end="2161600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">我們幾經辛苦才能逃跑出來</p>
<p begin="2168000000t" end="2180800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">原來如此</p>
<p begin="2187200000t" end="2212800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">諾曼，這段日子，你在哪裡</p>
<p begin="2265600000t" end="2303200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">我去了一個名為Lambda7214的地方</p>
<p begin="2304000000t" end="2321200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">那裡是實驗農場</p>
<p begin="2322000000t" end="2349200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">Lambda？　　實驗農場？</p>
<p begin="2350000000t" end="2361200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">那一晚</p>
<p begin="2364800000t" end="2386800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">媽媽帶我踏出了那道閘門之後</p>
<p begin="2398800000t" end="2422800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">就將我交給Lambda的研究員</p>
<p begin="2434400000t" end="2452000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">在那裡的鬼和大人</p>
<p begin="2452800000t" end="2477200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">會不停地讓我們試藥</p>
<p begin="2478000000t" end="2496800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">以及進行不同的實驗</p>
<p begin="2505200000t" end="2528800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">這麼做是為了大規模生產</p>
<p begin="2529600000t" end="2546000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">不同種類的高級肉</p>
<p begin="2557200000t" end="2570400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">在實驗過程中</p>
<p begin="2571200000t" end="2596000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">肌肉、神經系統，還有感官</p>
<p begin="2596800000t" end="2625200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">因為過度發達而長成畸形的人</p>
<p begin="2630800000t" end="2654400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">在那裡為數不少</p>
<p begin="2661200000t" end="2686800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">所以你們剛才才會那麼厲害嗎</p>
<p begin="2687600000t" end="2710800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">身為人類也能將鬼殺死</p>
<p begin="2711600000t" end="2738800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">沒錯，他們全部都是在Lambda</p>
<p begin="2739600000t" end="2756800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">接受實驗的人</p>
<p begin="2757600000t" end="2783200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">那麼就是你也一樣</p>
<p begin="2790000000t" end="2812800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">接受過那些實驗嗎</p>
<p begin="2813600000t" end="2840000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">在那裡，他們只讓我做了一些測驗</p>
<p begin="2840800000t" end="2855200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">所以不用擔心</p>
<p begin="2856000000t" end="2875600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">那你是如何逃走出來的</p>
<p begin="2882000000t" end="2905600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">全靠米涅瓦先生的支援者幫忙</p>
<p begin="2906400000t" end="2916800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">破壞Lambda</p>
<p begin="2917600000t" end="2946800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">我和食用兒童才能逃脫</p>
<p begin="2947600000t" end="2958400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">支援者？</p>
<p begin="2959200000t" end="2984800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">對，他說自己名叫蘇米</p>
<p begin="2985600000t" end="3018400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">就是他將那枝筆交給克羅妮修女的</p>
<p begin="3028400000t" end="3055600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">不過那個人已經被殺死了</p>
<p begin="3061200000t" end="3083600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">原來除了米涅瓦先生…</p>
<p begin="3084400000t" end="3102400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">還有其他支援者</p>
<p begin="3108400000t" end="3128000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">不過大家不用擔心</p>
<p begin="3128800000t" end="3150400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">我利用Lambda的實驗數據</p>
<p begin="3151200000t" end="3185200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">發明了一種可以令鬼退化的藥物</p>
<p begin="3186000000t" end="3197600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">退化？</p>
<p begin="3198400000t" end="3238000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">你們有想過為何鬼要吃人類嗎</p>
<p begin="3251600000t" end="3265600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">為甚麼</p>
<p begin="3266400000t" end="3295600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">因為不這麼做就無法維持下去</p>
<p begin="3308800000t" end="3320800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">維持甚麼</p>
<p begin="3326400000t" end="3353200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">鬼之所以有不同的形態及外貌</p>
<p begin="3354000000t" end="3369600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">是取決於吃了甚麼</p>
<p begin="3375600000t" end="3401600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">他們會吸收食物的外形及能力</p>
<p begin="3402400000t" end="3427200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">就是說鬼要透過吃人</p>
<p begin="3428000000t" end="3454400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">才能維持現在的形態及智力</p>
<p begin="3458800000t" end="3471600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">所以才吃人腦嗎</p>
<p begin="3472400000t" end="3506400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">沒錯，要我們不停地接受測驗</p>
<p begin="3507200000t" end="3516000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">主要的目的</p>
<p begin="3516800000t" end="3550800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">是為了令我們的腦袋更加發達</p>
<p begin="3551600000t" end="3578000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">就是說如果他們不吃人…</p>
<p begin="3585600000t" end="3622000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">那麼他們就會變成野生鬼那樣嗎</p>
<p begin="3622800000t" end="3642400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">野生鬼不是一樣危險嗎</p>
<p begin="3643200000t" end="3671600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">你錯了，應付野生鬼的勝算</p>
<p begin="3672400000t" end="3698000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">無論如何都高於應付高智慧的鬼</p>
<p begin="3698800000t" end="3723600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">還有，鬼只要失去智力</p>
<p begin="3724400000t" end="3746800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">他們之間就會互相殘殺</p>
<p begin="3747600000t" end="3769600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">我正在大量製造藥物</p>
<p begin="3770400000t" end="3788000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">不過以我手上的份量</p>
<p begin="3788800000t" end="3808400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">也足夠令這條村子的鬼</p>
<p begin="3809200000t" end="3833600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">集體退化成為野生鬼</p>
<p begin="3834400000t" end="3856000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">只要我的計劃順利就行了</p>
<p begin="3861600000t" end="3880000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">當鬼接觸過那種藥物一次</p>
<p begin="3880800000t" end="3903600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">就永遠沒辦法回復智力</p>
<p begin="3904400000t" end="3936000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">到時候，他們不僅會互相殘殺</p>
<p begin="3936800000t" end="3969600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">甚至連農場也不可以繼續經營下去</p>
<p begin="3976000000t" end="4001200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">我被關在Lambda時一直想著一件事</p>
<p begin="4008000000t" end="4028800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">在我們發現孤兒院的真相時</p>
<p begin="4029600000t" end="4047600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">艾瑪，你曾經說過</p>
<p begin="4048400000t" end="4064400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">「外面沒有就自己創造吧」</p>
<p begin="4065200000t" end="4086800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">「創造人類可以生存的地方」</p>
<p begin="4087600000t" end="4105200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">「由我們來改變世界」</p>
<p begin="4110800000t" end="4133200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">這個就是你想要的逃走計劃</p>
<p begin="4140400000t" end="4177600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">我也想創造家人和同伴</p>
<p begin="4178400000t" end="4207200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">每個食用兒童可以笑著生活的未來</p>
<p begin="4208000000t" end="4238400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">以後我想跟艾瑪、雷和大家</p>
<p begin="4239200000t" end="4254800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">一起生活下去</p>
<p begin="4255600000t" end="4265600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">我想了很久</p>
<p begin="4266400000t" end="4286400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">用甚麼方式去做是最好的</p>
<p begin="4292000000t" end="4306400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">最後得出的答案</p>
<p begin="4321600000t" end="4340800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">就是令鬼徹底滅絕</p>
<p begin="4347200000t" end="4368800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">以後不會再有夢幻島</p>
<p begin="4369600000t" end="4385200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">我們就在這個世界</p>
<p begin="4386000000t" end="4404800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">打造屬於人類的樂園</p>
<p begin="4405600000t" end="4419600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">太好了…</p>
<p begin="4420400000t" end="4444400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">這樣就可以救出菲爾他們了</p>
<p begin="4445200000t" end="4473200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">就是說以後的日子都不用逃避鬼了</p>
<p begin="4474000000t" end="4486400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">太好了</p>
