<p begin="4623600000t" end="4637600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">對，很好</p>
<p begin="4655600000t" end="4684000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">對，真的太好了</p>
<p begin="4693600000t" end="4704400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">太好了</p>
<p begin="4711200000t" end="4736400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">不過我們的時間不多了</p>
