<p begin="4834000000t" end="4853200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">那這個秘密基地…</p>
<p begin="4854000000t" end="4875600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">所以我想把握時間</p>
<p begin="4876400000t" end="4894000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">儘快執行這個計劃</p>
<p begin="4904400000t" end="4915200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">儘快執行？</p>
<p begin="4926000000t" end="4939200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">只要我發出指令</p>
<p begin="4940000000t" end="4956800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">第二天就可以執行</p>
<p begin="4957600000t" end="4977200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">第二天？　　真的嗎</p>
<p begin="4978000000t" end="4986800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">第一步</p>
<p begin="4987600000t" end="5012400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">是要令這條村子的鬼全部退化</p>
