<p begin="5041200000t" end="5068000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">就開始大規模攻擊其他城市</p>
<p begin="5068800000t" end="5084800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">將鬼一舉殲滅</p>
<p begin="5095600000t" end="5129600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">不僅要救菲爾，還要解放所有農場</p>
<p begin="5136400000t" end="5148400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">我們的存在</p>
<p begin="5149190000t" end="5169600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">不再是為了成為鬼的大餐</p>
<p begin="5177600000t" end="5200000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">而是為了得到自由及安全</p>
