<p begin="5214800000t" end="5234400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">沒有你，我們甚麼都做不到</p>
<p begin="5241590000t" end="5271600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">幸好有諾曼，終於有進展了</p>
<p begin="5284800000t" end="5304400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">我知道你們在這裡</p>
<p begin="5305200000t" end="5322800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">一定生活得很辛苦吧</p>
<p begin="5323600000t" end="5339600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">待作戰結束之後</p>
<p begin="5342000000t" end="5369600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">我們就搬去蘇米為我們準備的基地</p>
<p begin="5370400000t" end="5397200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">那裡不僅有床鋪和食物，還有浴室</p>
<p begin="5398000000t" end="5407600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">真的嗎</p>
<p begin="5408400000t" end="5432400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">厲害，就像避難所那樣</p>
<p begin="5433200000t" end="5464000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">謝謝你，諾曼…</p>
<p begin="5482800000t" end="5503200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">以後大家就不用再提心吊膽</p>
<p begin="5504000000t" end="5525200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">可以一覺睡到天亮了</p>
<p begin="5531600000t" end="5547200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">那麼我要先回去了</p>
<p begin="5548000000t" end="5572800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">這個是我的地址　　好吧</p>
<p begin="5709600000t" end="5736800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">坦白說，我現在還是不敢相信</p>
<p begin="5737600000t" end="5755600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">諾曼還活著的事</p>
<p begin="5763200000t" end="5788400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">還以為永遠都見不到他</p>
<p begin="5789200000t" end="5803600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">現在太好了</p>
<p begin="5809600000t" end="5832000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">你真的覺得好嗎</p>
<p begin="5844000000t" end="5861200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">我指諾曼的作戰計劃</p>
<p begin="5874400000t" end="5900400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">我想你不想這麼做</p>
<p begin="5917200000t" end="5940800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">怎麼會？怎麼會不想</p>
<p begin="5946000000t" end="5962000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">如果滅絕所有鬼</p>
<p begin="5962800000t" end="5989600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">以後就不用再逃走或躲起來了</p>
<p begin="5990400000t" end="6026000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">但這個不是你渴望看到的未來</p>
<p begin="6104800000t" end="6121200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">我很奇怪嗎</p>
<p begin="6167600000t" end="6200400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">坦白說，其實我不想殺死鬼</p>
<p begin="6221400000t" end="6240600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">我很奇怪嗎</p>
<p begin="6241400000t" end="6265800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">明明所有人聽到都覺得開心</p>
<p begin="6266600000t" end="6293400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">而他們開心的原因不是為了自己</p>
<p begin="6294200000t" end="6304200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">他們是替我開心</p>
<p begin="6305000000t" end="6321400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">以後不用這麼辛苦</p>
<p begin="6327800000t" end="6387800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">我不想被鬼吃，也不想有人被鬼吃</p>
<p begin="6392600000t" end="6407800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">明明很討厭被出欄</p>
<p begin="6413000000t" end="6448600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">也很討厭被當成獵物被鬼追捕獵殺</p>
<p begin="6459400000t" end="6485400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">明知道鬼是敵人，但是我…</p>
<p begin="6497400000t" end="6515000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">來到這裡才明白</p>
<p begin="6520200000t" end="6541000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">鬼跟人一樣有名字</p>
<p begin="6548600000t" end="6568600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">他們懂得獨立思考</p>
<p begin="6569400000t" end="6588200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">以及有重要的家人</p>
<p begin="6598200000t" end="6628600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">因為是敵人，就殺死他們？</p>
<p begin="6629400000t" end="6653800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">真的沒有趕盡殺絕以外的方法嗎</p>
<p begin="6662600000t" end="6692200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">更何況穆吉卡是我們的朋友</p>
<p begin="6699000000t" end="6733400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">你有這種想法，為何剛才不說出來</p>
<p begin="6753400000t" end="6767400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">我說不出口</p>
<p begin="6775800000t" end="6799400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">我想選擇一條沒有紛爭的路</p>
<p begin="6802200000t" end="6835400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">但大家渴望的是一個鬼滅絕的未來</p>
<p begin="6838600000t" end="6864200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">何況不管如何選擇，結果也一樣</p>
<p begin="6865000000t" end="6882600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">如果鬼一定要靠不斷地吃人</p>
<p begin="6883400000t" end="6900200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">才能維持形態</p>
<p begin="6903400000t" end="6926600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">那如果我們去了人類世界</p>
<p begin="6927400000t" end="6947800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">他們最後也會被滅絕</p>
<p begin="6957400000t" end="6975800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">我想選擇第三條路</p>
<p begin="6976600000t" end="7010200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">但我完全想不出來，怎麼辦？雷</p>
<p begin="7026200000t" end="7039400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">我也不知道</p>
<p begin="7055000000t" end="7074600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">我們甚麼都做不到</p>
<p begin="7075400000t" end="7097000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">也沒有反駁的餘地</p>
<p begin="7102200000t" end="7121000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">諾曼說得沒錯</p>
<p begin="7134600000t" end="7167000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">對了，就算絞盡腦汁也想不出來</p>
<p begin="7181400000t" end="7196600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">這是甚麼意思</p>
<p begin="7197400000t" end="7218200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">剛才你讓我說出自己的想法</p>
<p begin="7219000000t" end="7241000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">你能想到解決方法嗎　　想不到</p>
<p begin="7241800000t" end="7266200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">那麼你有甚麼建議嗎　　沒有</p>
<p begin="7267000000t" end="7283400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">那你為何要問我</p>
<p begin="7284200000t" end="7303000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">讓我說了這麼多</p>
<p begin="7303800000t" end="7316600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">人家本來打算讓這件事</p>
<p begin="7317400000t" end="7338600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">永遠埋在心底的</p>
<p begin="7339400000t" end="7356600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">但你很快就說了出來</p>
<p begin="7363400000t" end="7393800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">我見你說得很流暢，滔滔不絕</p>
<p begin="7394600000t" end="7416200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">如果你真的想永遠埋在心底</p>
<p begin="7417000000t" end="7435800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">就應該寧死也不說</p>
<p begin="7436600000t" end="7454600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">那就證明你還沒死心吧</p>
<p begin="7470600000t" end="7487800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">再遇上這種情況</p>
<p begin="7488600000t" end="7513000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">你也會像剛才那樣默不作聲</p>
<p begin="7513800000t" end="7539400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">到忍耐到一個程度就會爆發</p>
<p begin="7544600000t" end="7559400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">最頭痛的是</p>
<p begin="7560200000t" end="7593800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">你專門會選擇在最差的時機才爆發</p>
<p begin="7594600000t" end="7618600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">而且會一個人向著有麻煩的位置</p>
<p begin="7619400000t" end="7629400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">衝過去</p>
<p begin="7635800000t" end="7645800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">這樣的話</p>
<p begin="7646600000t" end="7674600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">很容易會連累大家都有危險</p>
<p begin="7675400000t" end="7697000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">接著諾曼就會被你牽連</p>
<p begin="7697800000t" end="7711800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">當然我也會</p>
<p begin="7712600000t" end="7727400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">所以我還是勸你一句</p>
<p begin="7728200000t" end="7746600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">有甚麼意見就說出來</p>
<p begin="7747400000t" end="7762200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">而且這次事關重大</p>
<p begin="7763000000t" end="7778600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">會牽連很多東西</p>
<p begin="7779400000t" end="7795400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">如果現在勉強說贊成</p>
<p begin="7796200000t" end="7816200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">到時你一定會後悔　　是</p>
<p begin="7817000000t" end="7844200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">雖然我贊成令鬼滅絕的做法</p>
<p begin="7850200000t" end="7867000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">但你卻不是這麼想</p>
<p begin="7867800000t" end="7897400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">所以你回去好好想清楚吧</p>
<p begin="7904600000t" end="7928600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">艾瑪，你究竟想怎麼做</p>
<p begin="7945000000t" end="7961000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">我不想鬼滅絕</p>
<p begin="7961800000t" end="7986600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">我想選擇一條沒有紛爭的路</p>
<p begin="7987400000t" end="8021000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">但單靠這種想法根本無法改變現狀</p>
<p begin="8021800000t" end="8037000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">所以我真的不知道應該怎麼做</p>
<p begin="8037800000t" end="8052600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">才是正確的</p>
<p begin="8053400000t" end="8075000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">那麼去跟諾曼談吧</p>
<p begin="8075800000t" end="8092200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">順便問他剛才那個問題</p>
<p begin="8093000000t" end="8106200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">跟諾曼談？</p>
<p begin="8107000000t" end="8128200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">我連自己想怎樣也不知道</p>
<p begin="8129000000t" end="8151400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">就是要趁你還猶豫不決</p>
<p begin="8152200000t" end="8174600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">待你按捺不住時再談就太遲了</p>
<p begin="8178200000t" end="8206200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">何況他又不是外人，他是諾曼</p>
<p begin="8207000000t" end="8239400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">他在我們心目中一直是無可取代的</p>
<p begin="8246600000t" end="8257800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">對</p>
<p begin="8258600000t" end="8296600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">還有，我們也不可以丟下他們不管</p>
<p begin="8317000000t" end="8332200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">孫居和穆吉卡？</p>
<p begin="8333000000t" end="8369400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">沒錯，至少他們從來都沒吃過人類</p>
<p begin="8370200000t" end="8398600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">但孫居和穆吉卡的形態是人類</p>
<p begin="8399400000t" end="8418600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">而且智力也很高</p>
<p begin="8419400000t" end="8440600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">有可能是他們說謊</p>
<p begin="8441400000t" end="8470200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">或他們是就算不用吃人</p>
<p begin="8471000000t" end="8484200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">也可以維持人類的形態</p>
<p begin="8485000000t" end="8516600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">以及智力的少數特別種</p>
<p begin="8517400000t" end="8546200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">如果所有鬼都像孫居和穆吉卡那樣</p>
<p begin="8547000000t" end="8573000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">說不定人類跟鬼就可以共存了</p>
<p begin="8580200000t" end="8602200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">你覺得諾曼知道這件事嗎</p>
<p begin="8603000000t" end="8614600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">很難說</p>
<p begin="8615400000t" end="8646600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">不過如果他不知道就糟糕了</p>
<p begin="8647400000t" end="8663800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">難道不是嗎</p>
<p begin="8664600000t" end="8682600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">諾曼研發出來的藥物</p>
<p begin="8683400000t" end="8704200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">暫時還不知道對特別種是否有效</p>
<p begin="8717000000t" end="8737000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">如果諾曼知道這件事</p>
<p begin="8737800000t" end="8749800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">或許可以問到</p>
<p begin="8750600000t" end="8770600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">為何會有特別種的鬼存在</p>
<p begin="8776200000t" end="8795800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">然後沿著線索尋找下去</p>
<p begin="8799000000t" end="8823800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">或許會找到人類跟鬼共存的方法</p>
<p begin="8824600000t" end="8833400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">雷</p>
<p begin="8834200000t" end="8855000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">不過現在最重要的是</p>
<p begin="8855800000t" end="8871400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">要在諾曼實行計劃之前</p>
<p begin="8872200000t" end="8888200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">跟他好好談一下</p>
<p begin="8900600000t" end="8927800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">坦白說，我覺得人類跟鬼共存</p>
<p begin="8928600000t" end="8946600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">簡直是天方夜譚</p>
<p begin="8947400000t" end="8974600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">鬼一旦看到人就會發瘋似的撲過去</p>
<p begin="8980200000t" end="8996200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">因為這是天性</p>
<p begin="8997000000t" end="9023000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">但孫居他們始終對我們有恩</p>
<p begin="9023800000t" end="9050200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">就由你作主吧，我們會支持你</p>
<p begin="9055800000t" end="9069800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">無論你選哪一條路</p>
<p begin="9070600000t" end="9085000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">我都對你有信心</p>
<p begin="9087800000t" end="9117400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">挑戰不可能不是你的強項嗎</p>
<p begin="9118200000t" end="9138200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">創造一個不會後悔的未來吧</p>
<p begin="9143800000t" end="9167800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">好，很感謝你</p>
<p begin="9168600000t" end="9185400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">我現在整個人放輕鬆了</p>
<p begin="9186200000t" end="9197000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">這麼快？</p>
<p begin="9301400000t" end="9313000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">哪位</p>
<p begin="9321400000t" end="9341400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">你們一定是老闆在…</p>
<p begin="9347000000t" end="9378600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">叫甚麼恩寵農場的同伴吧</p>
<p begin="9379400000t" end="9390200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">恩典農場</p>
<p begin="9391000000t" end="9414600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">我叫雷　　我叫艾瑪</p>
<p begin="9415400000t" end="9445400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">昨天真的很感謝你們出手救我們</p>
<p begin="9456200000t" end="9481800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">替你解決鬼的人叫薩吉，不是我們</p>
<p begin="9482600000t" end="9492600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">他跟老闆去了鬼的…</p>
<p begin="9493400000t" end="9516200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">老闆不用多久就會回來</p>
<p begin="9517000000t" end="9531000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">你們進去等一會吧</p>
<p begin="9569000000t" end="9583800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">我叫希斯洛</p>
<p begin="9584600000t" end="9599400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">她就是芭芭拉</p>
<p begin="9605000000t" end="9632600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">而這位就是智者文森特了</p>
<p begin="9633400000t" end="9643800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">你們好</p>
<p begin="9644600000t" end="9684600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">對了，你們說的老闆就是諾曼嗎</p>
<p begin="9685400000t" end="9705400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">不是他還會是誰</p>
<p begin="9706200000t" end="9735800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">感覺跟我認識的他截然不同</p>
<p begin="9745000000t" end="9763400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">他以前不是這樣的嗎</p>
<p begin="9764200000t" end="9788200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">你們是一起長大的家人嗎</p>
<p begin="9789000000t" end="9803800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">他以前是怎樣的</p>
<p begin="9804600000t" end="9834200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">你們所說的諾曼給你甚麼感覺</p>
<p begin="9835000000t" end="9846600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">該怎麼說</p>
<p begin="9847400000t" end="9878200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">諾曼既溫柔，又聰明</p>
<p begin="9879000000t" end="9907000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">他的笑容給人一種很溫暖的感覺</p>
<p begin="9907800000t" end="9931400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">溫暖？　　笑容嗎</p>
<p begin="9932200000t" end="9952200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">跟現在完全不同…</p>
<p begin="9957400000t" end="9973000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">真的一點也不像嗎</p>
<p begin="9973800000t" end="9997000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">那麼現在的諾曼給人甚麼感覺</p>
<p begin="9997800000t" end="10015000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">嚴肅　　冬天</p>
<p begin="10015800000t" end="10038600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">皇帝　　皇帝？</p>
<p begin="10039400000t" end="10056200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">多說一些吧</p>
<p begin="10057000000t" end="10079000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">他小時候有甚麼糗事</p>
<p begin="10079800000t" end="10102200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">睡覺時尿床算是嗎</p>
<p begin="10103000000t" end="10118200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">他小時候身體很差</p>
<p begin="10119000000t" end="10136600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">經常要去醫療室</p>
<p begin="10148200000t" end="10170200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">感覺真的很奇怪</p>
<p begin="10173800000t" end="10192200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">自從被他從Lambda救出來</p>
<p begin="10193000000t" end="10201800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">他給我們的感覺</p>
<p begin="10202600000t" end="10222600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">一直都是一個完美的天才</p>
<p begin="10227400000t" end="10266190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">但你也說得對，老闆真的很溫柔</p>
<p begin="10267000000t" end="10287000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">如果老闆當時沒有救我們</p>
<p begin="10287800000t" end="10313000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">我想我們早已死在那個地方</p>
<p begin="10313800000t" end="10333800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">對，不僅是Lambda</p>
<p begin="10343000000t" end="10365400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">其他量產型農場裡的食用兒童</p>
<p begin="10366190000t" end="10377400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">他也救出來了</p>
<p begin="10378190000t" end="10395400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">並安置在安全的地方</p>
<p begin="10405790000t" end="10414200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">救出他們之後</p>
<p begin="10415000000t" end="10437800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">就假裝成被鬼搶掠過那樣</p>
<p begin="10438590000t" end="10459400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">老闆為了達到目標真的很努力</p>
<p begin="10460200000t" end="10476190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">經常不眠不休</p>
<p begin="10493000000t" end="10513000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">真的很期待</p>
<p begin="10513800000t" end="10542200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">很想快點將那些鬼全都殺清光</p>
<p begin="10545800000t" end="10568200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">每當我殺死一隻鬼</p>
<p begin="10569000000t" end="10596600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">我的內心就會覺得特別痛快</p>
<p begin="10607800000t" end="10632600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">對，我也一樣</p>
<p begin="10633400000t" end="10659400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">但殺掉也不夠，還要吃掉他們的肉</p>
<p begin="10660200000t" end="10678600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">這樣才能發洩心頭之恨</p>
<p begin="10685800000t" end="10708600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">難道你手上的肉就是…</p>
<p begin="10709400000t" end="10745400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">猜對了，這是被我殺死的鬼的肉</p>
<p begin="10746200000t" end="10763800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">何須大驚小怪</p>
<p begin="10764600000t" end="10788600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">沒理由只有我們被鬼吃</p>
<p begin="10789400000t" end="10796200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">直到現在</p>
<p begin="10797000000t" end="10817000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">我的腦子和身體也無法磨滅</p>
<p begin="10817800000t" end="10839400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">他們在Lambda對我做過的事</p>
<p begin="10845800000t" end="10876600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">每一天…都好像在地獄</p>
<p begin="10877400000t" end="10903000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">用地獄來形容太簡單了</p>
<p begin="10903800000t" end="10926200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">很多小孩要麼捱不住死了</p>
<p begin="10927000000t" end="10939400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">要麼就被殺</p>
<p begin="10940200000t" end="10961400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">我們簡直連垃圾也不如</p>
<p begin="10962200000t" end="10983800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">所以光是殺死他們又怎麼足夠</p>
<p begin="10990200000t" end="11029800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">我要每隻鬼都嘗嘗我們經歷過的事</p>
<p begin="11040200000t" end="11057800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">為何這副表情</p>
<p begin="11058600000t" end="11075400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">你不開心嗎</p>
<p begin="11076200000t" end="11091000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">身為食用兒童</p>
<p begin="11091800000t" end="11123000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">別告訴我你不想殺死那些鬼</p>
<p begin="11123800000t" end="11154600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">對了，你們來找老闆有甚麼事</p>
<p begin="11155400000t" end="11179800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">不會是想用甚麼噁心的歪理</p>
<p begin="11180600000t" end="11203800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">來說服老闆改變計劃吧</p>
<p begin="11204600000t" end="11219800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">冷靜點吧，芭芭拉</p>
<p begin="11220600000t" end="11245800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">鬼是怪物，本來就應該滅絕</p>
<p begin="11246600000t" end="11264200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">別再說了，芭芭拉</p>
<p begin="11299800000t" end="11311400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">可惡</p>
<p begin="11344600000t" end="11357000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">不好意思</p>
<p begin="11360600000t" end="11387400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">但我和希斯洛的想法也跟她相同</p>
<p begin="11393400000t" end="11415400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">鬼是應該要被滅絕的</p>
<p begin="11416200000t" end="11435800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">在我們聊天的同時</p>
<p begin="11436600000t" end="11451000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">孤兒院的兄弟姐妹</p>
<p begin="11451800000t" end="11471000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">被當成貨物般送走</p>
<p begin="11471800000t" end="11489400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">所以一秒也不能拖延</p>
<p begin="11490200000t" end="11519800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">必須儘快摧毀農場把他們救出來</p>
<p begin="11524600000t" end="11537800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">我想你們也應該</p>
<p begin="11538600000t" end="11564200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">在孤兒院有家人等著你們拯救吧</p>
<p begin="11571000000t" end="11595800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">所以令鬼滅絕是最好的方法</p>
<p begin="11612600000t" end="11639400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">文森特、希斯洛，最後的實驗…</p>
<p begin="11656200000t" end="11672200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">艾瑪和雷？</p>
<p begin="11673000000t" end="11688200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">諾曼，是這樣的</p>
<p begin="11689000000t" end="11710600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">對不起，你們在這裡等我一會</p>
<p begin="11711400000t" end="11722600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">我很快回來</p>
<p begin="11771000000t" end="11795000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">你沒事吧　　沒事</p>
<p begin="11808200000t" end="11837400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">這麼做不是為了填飽肚子</p>
<p begin="11838200000t" end="11852600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">而是報仇</p>
<p begin="11879400000t" end="11900200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">不過他們這麼做的目的</p>
<p begin="11901000000t" end="11927800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">應該不僅是為了向鬼報仇的</p>
<p begin="11928600000t" end="11955400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">我猜他們最希望的是把家人救出來</p>
<p begin="11963800000t" end="11989000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">雖然很討厭鬼、很害怕鬼</p>
<p begin="11994600000t" end="12017400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">但也不可以因此而…</p>
<p begin="12018200000t" end="12048200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">很奇怪，我想不通</p>
<p begin="12049000000t" end="12072200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">對，但他們受的苦</p>
<p begin="12073000000t" end="12087400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">是我們想像不到的</p>
<p begin="12093000000t" end="12105400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">「別生氣了」</p>
<p begin="12106200000t" end="12123800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">這種說話我說不出口</p>
<p begin="12129400000t" end="12155000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">憎恨一旦開始了，就無法停止</p>
<p begin="12155800000t" end="12179800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">會好像雪球般越滾越大</p>
<p begin="12191800000t" end="12215800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">戰爭的起因通常就是這樣</p>
<p begin="12216600000t" end="12227800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">所以更加要…</p>
<p begin="12228600000t" end="12241000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">不好意思</p>
<p begin="12249800000t" end="12274200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">來找我有甚麼事嗎</p>
<p begin="12275000000t" end="12300600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">諾曼，我們有話想說</p>
<p begin="12301400000t" end="12315800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">是關於那個計劃的</p>
<p begin="12316600000t" end="12331000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">我們有些事情想問你</p>
<p begin="12337400000t" end="12355800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">另外有些情報想提供給你</p>
<p begin="12361000000t" end="12372200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">我明白了</p>
<p begin="12394200000t" end="12412600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">這瓶就是你說的藥物嗎</p>
<p begin="12413400000t" end="12434200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">就是它了</p>
<p begin="12435000000t" end="12448600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">諾曼</p>
<p begin="12449400000t" end="12490200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">這種藥物真的對所有鬼都有效嗎</p>
<p begin="12491000000t" end="12506600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">這是甚麼意思</p>
<p begin="12507400000t" end="12519800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">據我們所知</p>
<p begin="12520600000t" end="12545000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">有些鬼即使不吃人也不會退化</p>
<p begin="12552600000t" end="12568600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">我們擔心這種藥物</p>
<p begin="12569400000t" end="12584600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">不知道對那種鬼是否有效</p>
<p begin="12585400000t" end="12592600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">還有一件事…</p>
<p begin="12593400000t" end="12622200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">為甚麼你們會知道這件事</p>
<p begin="12633000000t" end="12652200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">是從哪裡聽來的</p>
<p begin="12653000000t" end="12669000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">是我們見過</p>
<p begin="12669800000t" end="12709000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">見過？是外形好像少女的鬼嗎</p>
<p begin="12714200000t" end="12725800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">諾曼</p>
<p begin="12726600000t" end="12738600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">不會吧</p>
<p begin="12761000000t" end="12786600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">難道邪血少女現在還活著</p>
<p begin="12832200000t" end="12858600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">(當你許下願望)</p>
<p begin="12859400000t" end="12885800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461">(月亮就灑下了影子)</p>
<p begin="12886600000t" end="12942600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462">(像魔法一般的夜晚必定融化無蹤)</p>
<p begin="13050600000t" end="13077000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463">(以澄澈響亮的聲音)</p>
<p begin="13077800000t" end="13104200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464">(風宣布了夜色來臨)</p>
<p begin="13105000000t" end="13131400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465">(藍色世界的一切)</p>
<p begin="13132200000t" end="13159000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466">(都在童話裡沉睡)</p>
<p begin="13159800000t" end="13185800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467">(你在半夢半醒之間)</p>
<p begin="13186600000t" end="13212600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468">(張開了閉著的眼瞼)</p>
<p begin="13213400000t" end="13237800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469">(比我心裡所想的)</p>
<p begin="13238600000t" end="13274200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470">(還要更加朦朧)</p>
<p begin="13290600000t" end="13339000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471">(如果這聲音能傳達)</p>
<p begin="13339800000t" end="13365800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472">(即使得不到回應　也想在你身旁)</p>
<p begin="13366600000t" end="13398200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473">(不想讓這個故事畫下句點)</p>
<p begin="13399000000t" end="13447800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474">(跨越長夜而去吧)</p>
<p begin="13448600000t" end="13473800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475">(跟你在一起　就再也不需要言語)</p>
<p begin="13474600000t" end="13521000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476">(如今只想確認彼此的溫度)</p>
<p begin="13521800000t" end="13557000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477">(讓我沉入不會醒的美夢吧)</p>
<p begin="13557800000t" end="13603800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478">(我們緊握著那雙手)</p>
<p begin="13604600000t" end="13633400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479">(靜靜地祈願著)</p>
</div>
